.TH "is_empty" 9 "is_empty" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
is_empty \- determine whether a buffer is empty (contains all 0xff).
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" is_empty
.BI "(void *buf "  ","
.BI "int len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "buf" 12
buffer to clean
.IP "len" 12
length of buffer
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function returns 1 if the buffer is empty (contains all 0xff) otherwise
0 is returned.
